rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Are friends going to do bashy-smashy
on the Holy Grail? Is there something
Momimi can do to help?

rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Momimi has to go back to HQ of
Pyrithium Trade Guild, you know.

rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It ruffle fluff to say it,
but Momimi will say farewell
to friends soon. Sadness!

rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0004
rows.name:
But fluff of Momimi ruffled not only
by sad feelings, but by many happy
memories found on streets of Iira.

rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0005
rows.name:
This happy land where Nopon, Iiran
and Blade can live together in
friendship. Very dear thing to Momimi.

rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0006
rows.name:
But Momimi will return to
Iira one day. Promise!

rows.label: tlk70000033_05_msg0007
rows.name:
And Momimi will see friends
again. So don't forget Momimi!
